Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.21,0:00:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}SMA enggak asyik sama sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.46,0:00:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau balik ke SMP saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bilang begitu terus, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak ada tempat senyaman rumah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.22,0:00:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah enggak ada\Nyang bilang begitu lagi, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.09,0:00:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukannya kau datang ke festival budaya\Nbareng teman-teman SMA-mu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.51,0:00:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka semua orang baik, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.52,0:00:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma enggak cocok\Nsama suasana sekolahnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terlalu membosankan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, suasananya tenang terus.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata orang konyolnya sedikit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutmu bagaimana perasaan kami?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudku bukan nilai akademisnya,\Ntapi suasananya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.40,0:00:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waktu pulang sekolah pas kelas tiga SMP\Nitu paling seru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.78,0:00:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sesi belajar bareng Yamada\Ndan Suzuki sepulang sekolah…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.62,0:00:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu asyik banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.58,0:00:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita cuma mengobrol, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma ingat kita terus\Nmenertawakan hal-hal konyol.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.25,0:00:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar! Itu yang paling seru!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.80,0:00:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Auranya mengintimidasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.30,0:00:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meskipun kita lagi siap-siap ujian,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ada rasa bebas karena enggak perlu ekskul\Nsepulang sekolah,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.72,0:00:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan emosi yang meluap\Nkarena enggak mau menyesal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:01:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sebelum lulus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.39,0:01:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Matahari terbenam menyinari kelas,\Nsuasana sentimental itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiba-tiba dia curhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.01,0:01:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi terus
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.06,0:01:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yamada punya pacar,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi, dia sering menghilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.56,0:01:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, itu bukan salahku, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terkadang pas malam hari,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.11,0:01:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku jalan-jalan ke arah SMP\Ntanpa alasan yang jelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau baik-baik saja?
