Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau makan apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau kari ayam.
