Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, dia juga…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kayaknya aku mulai menyukainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, bagaimana?
