Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang sebenarnya terjadi sama Yamada…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau yang memotret ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keren banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus bagaimana?\NAku gugup banget sampai enggak bisa ngomong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau menghubungiku pas liburan musim panas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku enggak pandai membalas pesan.
