Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang mau kau katakan tadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga minta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ponselku…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.52,0:05:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cuma kupakai buat menghubungi orang tuaku
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}atau sesekali mengirim pesan ke Hon\Ndan teman-teman cewek yang dekat denganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku selalu berpikir berlebihan\Ndan khawatir ngomong hal yang aneh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}atau bikin kesalahan,\Njadi, aku lama balasnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, aku cenderung\Nmengirim pesan yang panjang banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga mengkhawatirkan\Nkeheningan canggung di telepon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku terus berpikir berlebihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bukan karena aku enggak suka, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berpikir berlebihan karena takut gagal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Andai aku enggak terlalu banyak berpikir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku benar-benar kebalikannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang pas terima balasan,\Njadi, langsung kubalas tanpa berpikir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa kau enggak ngomong hal aneh, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudku,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.49,0:06:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku lebih santai daripada dugaanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak apa-apa kalau gagal.\NLagi pula, ini cuma aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau enggak perlu sebegitu sungkannya padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita kan seangkatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kesal, bilang saja, "Ini nyebelin."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau berisik, bilang saja,\N"Kau berisik banget, Bodoh."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku enggak bakal ngomong\Ndengan nada kayak begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Kau berisik"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.46,0:06:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku enggak seberkelas itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ri? Sial!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus pergi. Makasih, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa kita ngobrol lagi di sekolah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, sampai nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.19,0:06:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitulah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia perlahan melangkah maju tanpa sadar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suasana hatinya lagi bagus banget\Nsejak festival budaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah jelas dia mencari seseorang\Nselama ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku enggak bilang apa-apa, kok.\NAku enggak bakal mengejekmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yamada, kau mencari seseorang?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gapacho.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak ada komentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, jangan dipikirkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dipikir-pikir,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yamada dan Tani sebenarnya\Norang yang sangat baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pantas saja orang lain\Nbisa suka sama mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka mungkin bakal menerima\Nperasaan itu dengan baik juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, Taira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sifatmu beda dari dugaanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan memikirkan hal\Nyang enggak menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.20,0:07:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sahabat Yamada bilang SMP\Nitu seru banget, tapi SMA enggak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.41,0:07:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pada akhirnya,\Nitu cuma masalah perbandingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}SD dan SMP, yang enggak bisa kau pilih,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lebih terasa kayak neraka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kau bisa diterima di sana,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}itu sudah jadi hal yang bikin iri...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kau enggak ngomong sama sekali?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tertipu! Kau tertipu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kau tertipu! Kau tertipu!\N- Beraninya kau ganggu musikku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, jangan ketawa, dong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku enggak ketawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.28,0:08:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketawa saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Taira enggak jalan ke arah stasiun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.87,0:08:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Artinya kau kerja hari ini, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo mampir ke toserba dulu sebelum pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Setuju, Tani?\N- Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Boleh.\N- Apa maksudmu, "Boleh"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bakal ke sana sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bantu aku bikin es krim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami enggak punya mesin kayak begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, pas kalian berdua sampai,\Npegawai sif sebelumnya masih tugas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani, kau bisa nunggu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pulang sana!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang perlu dicemaskan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lucu, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau selalu datang pas sifku?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soalnya lebih seru kalau ada kau.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.77,0:08:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan begitu, Tani?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitukah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terserah, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku dapat hadiah\Ndari es loli yang baru kubeli!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat pulang sana!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Selamat pagi.\N- Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yamada...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus bagaimana? Menyapanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus inisiatif duluan?\NAku bisa, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak apa-apa kalau gagal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, ini cuma aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Nishi.\N- Astaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, begini…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah memberanikan diri\Nbuat nyapa duluan,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi kau malah mendahuluiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sampai harus memberanikan diri?\NLucu banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menertawakanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa mukamu begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kayaknya kalian akur.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari sudut pandangmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bagaimana perasaanmu ke Yamada?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa gugup, sih,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.06,0:10:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku enggak ngerti apa yang kurasakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perasaan apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sulit dipercaya,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ada orang yang benar-benar bilang begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa hatiku sakit banget?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kayak gitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak, enggak seindah itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan indah, sih…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejujurnya, aku enggak tahu\Napa jantungku berdebar
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}gara-gara Yamada
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}atau gara-gara situasinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini lebih realistis daripada dugaanku…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soalnya aku jarang ngobrol sama cowok.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku gugup banget sampai enggak tahu\Napa yang bikin aku gugup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Walaupun bukan Yamada,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku mungkin bakal sama gugupnya…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ngerti sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi asal kau tahu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lega kau bukan tokoh utama\Nyang terlalu bodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf. Tenang saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.24,0:11:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}enggak masalah kan kalau jantungmu berdebar\Ngara-gara situasinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukannya itu berarti bisa siapa saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}percuma terlalu dipikirin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Simpelnya, kalau itu situasi\Nyang bikin jantungmu berdebar,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}itu juga bakal terjadi sama orang lain,\Nbukan cuma Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu yang kau cemaskan, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau punya orang kayak gitu sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, enggak ada gunanya bandingkan\NYamada sama orang yang enggak ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Aku harus bagaimana kalau begitu?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu cuma pikiranmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak bakal ada habisnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daripada mencemaskan kemungkinan,\Nmending pikirkan kenyataannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau enggak memikirkan\Nperasaanmu ke dia saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya. Kau benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku harus cari cara\Nbuat ngobrol normal sama dia dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nah, itu intinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:11:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah cowok atau cewek,\NEnggak apa-apa, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}orang lain itu cuma manusia biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hon terkadang bisa agak menyeramkan, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.97,0:12:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasakan dirimu pelan-pelan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jantungmu berdebar karena kau malu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau karena situasinya bikin kau lengah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau karena dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya bakal baik-baik saja\Nkalau kau sudah paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sama sekali enggak pemalu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku iri banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu bukan berarti pemalu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cenderung enggak suka orang asing,\Nbagiku cowok maupun cewek sama saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masa, sih…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makasih atas kerja kerasmu hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena dia selalu diam,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku jadi enggak tahu isi pikirannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku agak takut dan gugup.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi setelah ngobrol sebentar sama dia\Ndi festival budaya,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku enggak segugup sebelumnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Suzuki, kau lagi apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu masuk, lo,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ke gedung sekolah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu enggak masuk hitungan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu salah angin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan Nishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kapan kau temanan sama Nishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa salahnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, 'kan, Nishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa boleh kalau aku
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jalan pulang bareng kalian?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian berdua habis main bulu tangkis?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, bulu tangkis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak Klub Pulang juga bakal karatan
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalau enggak sesekali olahraga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kapan coba kau pernah gesit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan ngomong seolah kau profesional, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau melambat, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki yang mana yang kau bicarakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gitu saja bikin kau ketawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lucu banget dia langsung memikirkan\Nkebalikan dari "karatan".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Udaranya lumayan sejuk, ya.\NKeringatku jadi dingin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga, apa aku bau keringat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata kau tipe orang\Nyang peduli soal itu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti, dong!\NJangan langsung blak-blakan gitu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nishi, kau gampang banget ketawa, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Malu-maluin banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jantungku berdebar karena gugup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.10,0:14:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku ingin mengubahnya,\Ntapi enggak bisa menahannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa harus diubah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukannya ini bagus?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau enggak perlu mengubah apa pun, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma gugup…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kau khawatir berkeringat,\Nhabiskan saja satu botol ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aroma apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mint dingin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dingin banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apaan nih?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Badanku kedinginan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya aku enggak pakai lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa menghabiskannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau cuma mau menghabiskan stokmu saja, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menertawakan hal-hal sepele.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bikin suasana jadi seru.\NTapi itu juga karena Yamada pintar
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani, selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menyapanya dengan natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ngantuk banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani, selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apaan tuh, tadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani, kau lagi ngomongin apa sama Nishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nishi? Di mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak apa-apa. Aku cuma nyapa dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyapa itu normal, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau enggak melakukan apa-apa\Nyang bikin dia buru-buru pergi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:15:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nishi itu orangnya kayak bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau kan juga penjaga perpustakaan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi, kau pasti sudah lama kenal dia, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pasti sering ngobrol sama dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak sama sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masa, sih…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bilang edisi terbatas
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}roti goreng daging sapinya sudah habis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Taira, bisa ngobrol sebentar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ngobrol sama aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentang apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki kepo sama cewek yang jadi\Npenjaga perpustakaan bareng kau?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya dia punya niat tertentu,\Ntapi aku enggak ngerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cuma itu sih kemungkinannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia mencurigaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia mungkin berpikir kalian berdua dekat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia cemburu, tuh. Cemburu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku enggak melakukan apa-apa\Nyang bikin dia cemburu, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudku, sulit membayangkan\NSuzuki bakal berpikir kayak gitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kalau Suzuki benar-benar cemburu,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}berarti dia munafik.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani, kurasa wajar kalau kau marah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marah saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau bikin kami berantem?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau senang dia cemburu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya. Aku paham sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini memang sulit dibayangkan,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi kau berharap\Ndia mungkin beneran cemburu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kau enggak cukup percaya diri\Nbuat bilang begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitukah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak begitu, kok…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitukah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.89,0:17:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kalian berdua
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi akrab banget tanpa kami sadari.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku semenyeramkan itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jadi merasa agak bersalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.86,0:17:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bakal jaga\Nperpustakaan lagi hari ini, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nishi juga di sana, pastinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki, apa ada yang mengganggumu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku habis beli banyak barang!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.71,0:18:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keren banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yamada, lihat ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat, nih!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mantap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku melewatkan kesempatan buat nanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah menyapa Tani,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku malah kabur pas lihat Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal akhirnya aku bisa ngobrol\Nlebih luwes dari sebelumnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku malah mundur lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau senang dia cemburu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia gelisah, tapi dalam hati,\Naku malah senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bukan hubungan yang seimbang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudku...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meskipun enggak jelas\Natau kau masih memikirkannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalau ada yang mengganggumu,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bilang saja langsung.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga berpikir begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau ada yang mau kau sampaikan,\Nkuharap kau bilang langsung ke aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, aku enggak melakukan apa pun\Nyang bikin Suzuki gelisah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya bakal memalukan banget\Nkalau dicurigai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.82,0:19:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau ini terus berlanjut,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku pasti bakal menyesal\Nkayak pas liburan musim panas lalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lain kali aku enggak boleh kabur lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa niatnya?\NApa yang dia pikirkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cuma memikirkannya saja\Nenggak bakal memberiku jawaban.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Khawatir dan panik sendirian itu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}terlalu menyedihkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanti kalau kami ketemu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanti pas kami ketemu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus tanya ke dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus ngobrol baik-baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makasih atas kerja keras kalian hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kerja bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:19:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo ngomong sesuatu. Cepat ngomong sesuatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.11,0:20:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana, nih? Aku harus bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pas lihat dia,\Naku bahkan enggak berani menatap matanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau suka main gelembung sabun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami bosan bermain macam-macam mainan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kami lagi mengadakan\Nfestival meniup gelembung sabun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Festival meniup gelembung sabun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kau enggak keberatan, ini untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yamada bawa cairan gelembungnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuterima dengan senang hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kaku banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waktu itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:21:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nishi, kau gampang banget ketawa, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingat...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kayaknya aku mulai menyukainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.68,0:21:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Satu sekolah, beda kelas, introver?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.39,0:21:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukannya ini bagus?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.81,0:21:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau enggak perlu mengubah apa pun, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu Nishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terus, tadi pagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.74,0:21:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani, selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apaan tuh, tadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia kabur sambil tersipu malu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gara-gara dia lihat Yamada...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.12,0:21:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sudah jelas…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.25,0:21:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mereka saling suka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.51,0:21:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah aku berhasil menahan Yamada\Nsampai perpustakaan tutup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau menanyakan soal Nishi\Nke aku seharian ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau tahu lebih banyak soal dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.52,0:21:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soalnya aku mau temanan sama dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.52,0:22:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nishi itu orangnya kayak bagaimana, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.53,0:22:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi maksudnya benaran harfiah, ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.82,0:22:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Kau kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.99,0:22:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau enggak apa-apa? Kau sakit?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.16,0:22:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bunuh saja aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.28,0:22:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memangnya kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.16,0:22:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nishi, maafin aku, ya.\NSuzuki maksa banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.75,0:22:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak kok, ini seru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.54,0:22:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lakukan sesuatu ke Yamada, dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.50,0:22:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia kelihatan sudah berusaha keras banget.
